  "outcome": "Price retested the area and expanded higher as anticipated, confirming the ideal continuation.",
  "lessons": "An ideal continuation combines a POI tap, V-shaped recovery, and swift closure through opposing candles to form a protected swing. When the prior high is still untaken, expect further expansion toward that buyside liquidity.",
